title: Welcome
description: Crystal Urban provides world-class massage therapy in Pulaski WI. Call and start improving your health today: (715) 610-6544
cleaned_text: In today's world, becoming ill, injured, or aging in unanticipated ways can be a confusing and sometimes stressful reality. At Earth Integrated Medicine, LLC, we provide the highest quality of care by blending the tools of both Naturopathic and Chinese medicine in a functional medicine approach to identify the root cause of illness and formulate a plan based on your individual needs. With over 20 years of clinical experience, Dr. Urban offers down to earth options and natural treatments to optimize your health and the prevention of future disease and injury. It's about Options! You can request to schedule an appointment by calling 715-610-6544 or emailing dr.crystalurban@icloud.com. We do not accept text or other media platforms.
